{"tid":700626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【已經做咗8年】支那木馬李小加再獲續任港交所行政總裁3年  加薪3.5%","createTime":"2018-06-13T13:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T16:38:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5803c85d15c707c6a6436b82d7dc8725720a8d","tid":700626,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180613/large/1528879101_7d4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180613%2Flarge%2F1528879101_7d4b.jpg&h=f9aa3ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港交所（388）公布，董事局已批准行政總裁李小加續約，由今年10月16日起，至2021年10月15日，年期為三年，有關任命須待證監會書面核准作實。<br />\n<br />\n續約後，李小加年薪931.5萬元，較上一份合約每年900萬增加3.5%，但年薪只是「配菜」，花紅才是重點，李小加去年年薪連花紅等總計逾4,885.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n李小加於2009年10月加入港交所，並於2012年及2015年各續約三年，計及今次續約，李小加將任港交所行政總裁長達12年，成為港交所成立以來在位最長的行政總裁。另一位「長命」行政總裁為周文耀，他1991至97年任職當時的聯交所行政總裁，後在2003年重返港交所任職至2009年。"},{"pid":"3f4253401dd1aa601b7a34b394613de9bf73e9d6","tid":700626,"uid":3241,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"做左十幾年連廣東話都仲係唔識講<br />\n殖民都學下英國佬官學生必學中文先啦"},{"pid":"f3f629c39d6eb87de7c39b0db6846647d8f69480","tid":700626,"uid":68728,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾做得咁差都續? <br />\n<br />\n江交所呢隻世紀妖股連幾年前高位都上唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2a33a5044b4d7cf16e9c6bfec125eb246f87c2","tid":700626,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"續條垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f584e56c9265069a5b87be19de2d18f128dab9","tid":700626,"uid":151071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:20:14.000Z","msg":"成日比d 老千股上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"